com.interactivemesh.jfx.importer.x3d

Class X3dMetadataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.interactivemesh.jfx.importer.x3d.X3dMetadata
      • com.interactivemesh.jfx.importer.x3d.X3dMetadataSet

  • public final class X3dMetadataSet
extends X3dMetadata
    A set of XMetadata objects consisting of user data value objects and/or sets of user data. A XMetadataSet object allows the construction of complex user data structures.
    See Also:
    X3dMetadataValue
